  "title": "Coco kiss",
  "handle": "coco-kiss-perfume",
  "body_html": "<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">A soft, cozy gourmand that smells like a warm coconut dessert melting into your skin.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">What you’ll smell:</span><span class=\"s1\"><br>It opens creamy and milky with a toasted coconut vibe, slightly nutty and smooth—not overly sweet. As it settles, it turns into a warm vanilla with a hint of buttery richness, almost like coconut cream with a soft woody touch in the background. It’s subtle, comforting, and very “your skin but better.”</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">Notes:</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\">\n<span class=\"s3\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Top: Coconut cream</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li1\">\n<span class=\"s3\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Heart: Toasted praline</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li1\">\n<span class=\"s3\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Base: Vanilla, warm woods</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">Vibe:</span><span class=\"s1\"><br>Clean girl but cozy. Effortless, soft, and addictive—like warm skin after a beach shower.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">When to wear:</span><span class=\"s1\"><br>Perfect for daytime, casual outings, gym, or layering with deeper vanillas at night. Best in spring/summer but honestly works year-round if you like soft gourmands.</span></p>",
